``` 

## Notes

The `perSystem.apps` are defined within the `perSystem` attribute of the `flake.nix` outputs, which is generated by `flake-parts.lib.mkFlake`.   The `isDarwin` variable is used to conditionally select between macOS and Linux specific commands and targets.  The `homedir` and `hostname`/`username` variables are also used to construct paths and flake references dynamically.   

